{"type": "article", "id": 12385, "title": "自定义挂钩系列", "description": "", "date": "2015-07-21T07:42:31Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 17, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606071225106MxwDjlBkiuYLb2e.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t以色列设计师 Vered Venezia 推出了一套自定义挂钩系列，她提供给你各式各样的零件，而用户可以根据自己的喜好排列出不同的挂件，有落地式衣架，小物件托盘，墙壁小架子等等。她的设计灵感来自小时候玩过的玩具，试图用这样的方式吸引人们发挥创造力，自己动手的激情。<a href=\"https://www.behance.net/veredvenezia\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>可以查看她更多作品。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140134U3vnxGE8VFyNH1aQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.33981481\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140135sh3aFREDNoS6Wzik.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5712963\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140136VwFtPMEJ4RcI3uDm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5712963\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140137hxrSvBMlXEsLjUmH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.53425926\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201607261401386sHBgCTKi3L9qGVw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5712963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140138lMWRqDbgTAnKLBoi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.53796296\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140139xQOT6zPpk0GSatI7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5712963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}